          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="font-bold text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0">2.</span>Build the recipe in Free Calorie Track once</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="font-bold text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0">3.</span>Weigh the total finished dish, then log your portion as a fraction</li>
